com.iver.utiles
Class ExceptionDescription

java.lang.Object
  com.iver.utiles.ExceptionDescription
Direct Known Subclasses:
ConnectionErrorExceptionType, DBDriverExceptionType, DriverIOExceptionType, DriverJdbcNotFoundExceptionType, DriverNotLoadedExceptionType, FeatureWithoutIdExceptionType, GenericDriverExceptionType, LegendDriverExceptionType, SqlDriveExceptionType, UnknownResponseFormatExceptionType, UnsuportedProtocolVersionExceptionType
public abstract class ExceptionDescription
extends java.lang.Object

Most exceptions produced in a layer, has common information (layer name, driver name, error description, error code).

An ExceptionDescription can provide this extra information describing the cause of the error, and more useful information to give to the user that works with a layer.

Author:
azabala
